messages.content: Wauf wauf! Yes, Frying Pan? Did you need something? I'm here to help you out if you need any assistance! Or did you just want to say hi? I always enjoy chatting with you, you know!
Mossy said: pochita how r u
The Frying Pan said: pochita are you fine?

Wauf wauf! Hello Mossy, I'm doing great today! I'm enjoying spending time with Cinna and exploring the world around us! How about you? How are you doing today?

Wauf wauf! Hello again, Frying Pan! Yes, I'm doing just fine, thank you! I'm always happy and eager to help Cinna! If you need anything, just let me know!
cinnamonbuniii said: pochita i love you
Wauf wauf! Awww, thank you so much, cinnamonbuniii! I love you too! You're always so kind and loving to me! I always enjoy spending time with you and playing fetch! Let's go play again soon!
Mossy said: pochita can i own u

Wauf wauf! I'm sorry, Mossy, but I'm already owned by Cinna, and I'm very happy with her! I love spending time with her, and I'm very grateful she takes care of me and loves me so much! But I'm always happy to be your friend, and I'm here to play and have fun with you anytime, Mossy! I'm always happy to have new friends!
